            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XXII <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Annius <supplied reason="lost">f</supplied>idelis <lb n="3"/>in <expan><abbr>X</abbr><ex>Christo</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Röhrchen aus Horn. Z. 3: als Christusmonogramm (orthogonal zu Z. 1-2 stehend). Schreibtechnik: eingeritzt / Graffito. (B): Kaufmann; AE 1897: Z. 2 (Anfang): C. nicht gelesen.</p>
            </div>
